fr.xephi.authme.data.limbo

Class LimboPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.xephi.authme.data.limbo.LimboPlayer

  • public class LimboPlayer
extends Object
    Represents a player which is not logged in and keeps track of certain states (like OP status, flying) which may be revoked from the player until he has logged in or registered.
